Steven Greer is one of the world's foremost authorities on the subject of UFOs, extraterrestrial intelligence and technologies, and initiating peaceful contact with interstellar civilizations. For over 30 years, Dr. Greer has provided briefings for senior government officials across the globe, conducted numerous media interviews, and delivered hundreds of lectures. He has also written five books {https://trello.com/c/8TSpAMV0/2279-%F0%9F%93%9A-books-by-dr-steven-greer} and produced feature film documentaries {https://trello.com/c/ciyHhDAc/2283-%F0%9F%8E%A5-documentaries-by-dr-greer} that have been seen by hundreds of millions of people. Dr. Greer's relentless efforts towards the disclosure of classified UFO/ET information have inspired millions of supporters around the world.\n\n> Dr. Greer's career began as an emergency and trauma physician, where he worked as an emergency room doctor and ultimately served as Chairman of Emergency Medicine at Caldwell Memorial Hospital in Lenoir, North Carolina. In 1987, Dr. Greer became a member of the prestigious Alpha Omega Alpha Honor Medical Society {https://trello.com/c/DIS4M6C0/2281-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-is-a-member-of-alpha-omega-alpha}.\n\n> While Dr. Greer's interest in the UFO/ET theme began at an early age {https://trello.com/c/xk0nidWX/2103-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-describes-the-near-death-and-contact-experiences-of-his-youth}, his increased attention to the subject did not develop until well into his medical career. At that stage, Dr. Greer's ongoing personal research into UFOs, ETs, and new energy systems led him to the knowledge that information and technologies surrounding these subjects were being kept from both the public and the highest ranks of our government, through decades of highly classified programs. It was this alarming realization that inspired Dr. Greer to begin his focused work on disclosure.\n\n> Dr. Greer initiated his work in the UFO/ET area by founding the Center for the Study of Extra-Terrestrial Intelligence (CSETI) {https://trello.com/c/kPV4R8gJ/903-%F0%9F%8C%90-sirius-disclosure-cseti} in 1990. CSETI was established as a diplomatic and research-based organization to make peaceful contact with extraterrestrial civilizations. Soon after, Dr. Greer founded https://trello.com/c/QM5mVK4f/2098-%F0%9F%8F%9B%EF%B8%8F-the-disclosure-project-%F0%9F%97%A3%EF%B8%8F, a nonprofit research initiative aimed at publicly disclosing the extensive and deeply classified information about UFOs, extraterrestrial intelligence, and advanced energy and propulsion systems.\n\n> While CSETI continued its diplomatic efforts throughout the 1990s, https://trello.com/c/QM5mVK4f/2098-%F0%9F%8F%9B%EF%B8%8F-the-disclosure-project-%F0%9F%97%A3%EF%B8%8F made substantial progress towards the release of classified UFO/ET information, culminating in the groundbreaking National Press Club Disclosure Event {https://trello.com/c/lZHwyO4m/810-2001-national-press-club-event-initiated-by-dr-steven-greers-disclosure-project} in May, 2001. During this event, over 20 military, government, intelligence, and corporate witnesses presented compelling testimony regarding the existence of extraterrestrial visitations as well as the reverse engineering of their energy and propulsion systems by classified government projects. The event reached an audience of over one billion people through both real-time streaming and coverage on top-tier, global media outlets.\n\n> In addition to Dr. Greer's ongoing efforts towards peaceful extraterrestrial contact and classified information disclosure, he has worked extensively to bring together scientists, inventors and leaders across the globe to advance new, clean technology energy systems. Dr. Greer is one of the world's most recognized strategists focused on transforming our civilization from one of fossil-fuel reliance to that of clean, free energy systems.\n\n> Dr. Greer has been seen and heard by vast audiences worldwide on CBS, the BBC, The Discovery Channel, The History Channel (including the Ancient Aliens series), Thrive and through a variety of global news outlets and social media networks. Millions have seen his groundbreaking documentaries, Sirius (2013) {https://trello.com/c/Ra3w2d2H/2139-%F0%9F%8E%A5-sirius} and Unacknowledged (2017) {https://trello.com/c/NlEzu9uP/1868-%F0%9F%8E%A5-unacknowledged}, the latter of which yielded a companion book of the same name Overview\n----------------\n\nhttps://trello.com/c/4dFMjJpF/2089-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-steven-greer-%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F is indisputably the foremost authority on ET contact in the United States, having the most knowledge and interactions on the subject.\n\n👨‍🏫 He is an eloquent teacher on matters of contact; for instance:\nhttps://trello.com/c/TlloDiCa/2314-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-they-are-awake-we-are-awake-consciousness-is-the-singular-point-of-contact\nhttps://trello.com/c/kTknzbYm/1291-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-tools-for-making-et-contact-per-dr-greer\nhttps://trello.com/c/do0yMEjX/831-the-crossing-point-of-light-%F0%9F%92%A1\n\n💬 Dr. Greer is considered one of the \"five messiahs\" in Grant Cameron's Managing Magic metaphor and theory... while he is unlike some of the other \"messiahs\" described by the theory – in that Greer doesn't claim himself to be a \"messiah\" – he does function similarly to the others, by providing disclosure to the masses with substantial help from government connections.\n\n🗺️ Dr. Greer is from Charlotte, North Carolina; he now lives in Charlottesville, Virginia. Go figure.\n\n👀 Also check out https://trello.com/c/vvT4vjRf/2421-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-greers-official-biographical-summary-%F0%9F%93%9D.\n\n----\n\n⌚ Chronology\n----------------\n\n📅 On June 28, 1955, he was born in Charlotte, North Carolina.\n\n🌌 He had a near-death experience, and later, a direct contact experience, when he was young:\nhttps://trello.com/c/xk0nidWX/2103-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-describes-the-near-death-and-contact-experiences-of-his-youth\n🪐 He was raised a \"devout atheist\", as he puts it. As part of his near-death experience, he experienced what he describes as a \"god-type consciousness\". For this reason, he no longer considers himself atheist; although he is not religious either. He is not associated with any church; he is associated only with his own experience.\n💡 As part of his direct contact experience, he cocreated the https://trello.com/c/0mjbV10S/2132-ce-5-%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F protocol with the ETs present.\n\n🧘‍♂️ His experiences led him to practice transcendental meditation, and he became a meditation teacher.\n📅 In the summer of 1975, https://trello.com/c/DL43YVQt/2429-dr-greer-vectored-a-craft-during-a-meditation-teacher-training-in-the-swiss-alps-resulting-in-his-first-group-ce-5-sighting.\n📎 The attached photo is from this event.\n\n📅 In 1987, he became a member of the prestigious Alpha Omega Alpha Honor Medical Society (https://trello.com/c/DIS4M6C0/2281-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-is-a-member-of-alpha-omega-alpha).\n\n📅 In 1990, he founded CSETI (https://trello.com/c/kPV4R8gJ/903-%F0%9F%8C%90-sirius-disclosure-cseti).\n\n📅 In 1993, https://trello.com/c/Q8njPWeA/1184-the-rockefeller-initiative was started. Dr. Greer started https://trello.com/c/QM5mVK4f/2098-the-disclosure-project.\n\n📅 In 1995, he wrote the https://trello.com/c/YGy2CXl9/916-%F0%9F%93%96-cseti-working-group-manual-by-dr-steven-greer. On April 8, he gave a presentation in Denver, Colorado;\nhttps://trello.com/c/Uptbas0G/642-%F0%9F%93%91-white-house-lawn-%F0%9F%8F%9B%EF%B8%8F-transcript-from-denver-colorado-presentation-by-dr-steven-greer-on-april-8-1995\n\n📅 In 1997, https://trello.com/c/3ombpcMe/317-the-pentagon-1997-ufo-briefing-involving-miller-greer-mitchell-wilson-davis took place.\n\n📅 In 1998, Steven retired from his career as an emergency room physician. He wrote https://trello.com/c/do0yMEjX/831-the-crossing-point-of-light-%F0%9F%92%A1. In April, the https://trello.com/c/2IPEY47N/1186-cseti-project-starlight disclosure strategy was formed.\n\n📅 In 1999, he published https://trello.com/c/ETUUzBWa/2295-%F0%9F%93%98-extraterrestrial-contact-the-evidence-and-implications, including the excerpt, https://trello.com/c/pYY3Jqg2/917-%F0%9F%93%84-the-imperative-of-consciousness-by-dr-greer.\n\n📅 In 2001, he held the https://trello.com/c/lZHwyO4m/810-2001-national-press-club-event-initiated-by-dr-steven-greers-disclosure-project.\n\n📅 In 2006, he published https://trello.com/c/Z1zgvT7e/178-%F0%9F%93%98-hidden-truth-forbidden-knowledge-by-dr-steven-greer.\n\n📅 In 2009, he published https://trello.com/c/uOZLftDQ/2140-%F0%9F%93%98%F0%9F%93%80-contact-countdown-to-transformation.\n\n📅 In 2013, he released https://trello.com/c/Ra3w2d2H/2139-%F0%9F%8E%A5-sirius.\n\n📅 In April of 2014, https://trello.com/c/R59C88Gi/2538-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-discusses-zero-point-energy-overunity-devices-and-project-strategies.\n\n📅 In March of 2015, he presented his https://trello.com/c/287R8rvR/1183-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-untold-history-briefing-from-dr-steven-greer.\n\n📅 On November 21, 2015, he presented his https://trello.com/c/QRPrSttt/232-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-expos%C3%A9-of-the-national-security-state-dr-steven-greer.\n\n📅 In April of 2017, he released https://trello.com/c/NlEzu9uP/1868-%F0%9F%8E%A5-unacknowledged and https://trello.com/c/jecE4dIj/2640-%F0%9F%93%98-unacknowledged.\n\n📅 On August 5, 2019, he uploaded https://trello.com/c/pQRoOgnX/2259-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-explaining-ufo-phenomena-%F0%9F%8E%87.\n\n📅 On August 19, 2019, he uploaded https://trello.com/c/mdzP8Nxa/1345-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-remote-viewing-with-dr-steven-greer.\n\n📅 On March 28, 2020, he livestreamed a discussion with Jim Martin; in this list (see below) demonstrates that.\n\n👨‍🏫 He is an eloquent teacher on matters of contact; for instance:\nhttps://trello.com/c/TlloDiCa/2314-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-they-are-awake-we-are-awake-consciousness-is-the-singular-point-of-contact\nhttps://trello.com/c/kTknzbYm/1291-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-tools-for-making-et-contact-per-dr-greer\nhttps://trello.com/c/do0yMEjX/831-the-crossing-point-of-light-%F0%9F%92%A1\n\n💬 Dr. Greer is considered one of the \"five messiahs\" in Grant Cameron's Managing Magic metaphor and theory... while he is unlike some of the other \"messiahs\" described by the theory – in that Greer doesn't claim himself to be a \"messiah\" – he does function similarly to the others, by providing disclosure to the masses with substantial help from government connections.\n\n----\n\n⌚ Chronology\n----------------\n\n📅 On June 28, 1955, he was born in Charlotte, North Carolina.\n\n🌌 He had a near-death experience and direct contact experience when he was young:\nhttps://trello.com/c/xk0nidWX/2103-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-describes-the-near-death-and-contact-experiences-of-his-youth\nHe was raised a \"devout atheist\", as he puts it.\nAs part of his near-death experience, he experienced what he describes as a \"god-type consciousness\". For this reason, he no longer considers himself atheist; although he is not religious either. He is not associated with any church; he is associated only with his own experience.\nAs part of his direct contact experience, he cocreated the https://trello.com/c/0mjbV10S/2132-ce-5-%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F protocol with the ETs present.\n\n🧘‍♂️ His experiences led him to practice transcendental meditation, and he became a meditation teacher.\n📅 In the summer of 1975, during a meditation teacher training in the Swiss Alps, Dr. Greer vectored an ET craft that resulted in his first group https://trello.com/c/0mjbV10S/2132-ce-5-%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F sighting.\n⌚ This is covered at 1:19:54 in https://trello.com/c/BfBibK5F/807-close-encounters-of-the-fifth-kind-the-best-documentary-on-the-subject.\n📎 The attached photo is from this event.\n\n📅 In 1987, he became a member of the prestigious Alpha Omega Alpha Honor Medical Society; https://trello.com/c/DIS4M6C0/2281-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-is-a-member-of-alpha-omega-alpha\n\n📅 In 1990, he founded CSETI (https://trello.com/c/kPV4R8gJ/903-%F0%9F%8C%90-sirius-disclosure-cseti).\n\n📅 In 1993, he started https://trello.com/c/QM5mVK4f/2098-the-disclosure-project.\n\n📅 In 1995, he wrote the https://trello.com/c/YGy2CXl9/916-%F0%9F%93%96-cseti-working-group-manual-by-dr-steven-greer.\n\n📅 In 1998, Steven retired from his career as an emergency room physician. summary:\n----------------\n\n> Dr. Steven Greer is one of the world's foremost authorities on the subject of UFOs, extraterrestrial intelligence and technologies, and initiating peaceful contact with interstellar civilizations. For over 30 years, Dr. Greer has provided briefings for senior government officials across the globe, conducted numerous media interviews, and delivered hundreds of lectures. He has also written five books (https://trello.com/c/8TSpAMV0/2279-%F0%9F%93%9A-books-by-dr-steven-greer) and produced feature film documentaries (https://trello.com/c/ciyHhDAc/2283-%F0%9F%8E%A5-documentaries-by-dr-greer) that have been seen by hundreds of millions of people. Dr. Greer's relentless efforts towards the disclosure of classified UFO/ET information have inspired millions of supporters around the world.\n\n> Dr. Greer's career began as an emergency and trauma physician, where he worked as an emergency room doctor and ultimately served as Chairman of Emergency Medicine at Caldwell Memorial Hospital in Lenoir, North Carolina. In 1987, Dr. Greer became a member of the prestigious Alpha Omega Alpha Honor Medical Society (https://trello.com/c/DIS4M6C0/2281-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-is-a-member-of-alpha-omega-alpha).\n\n> While Dr. Greer's interest in the UFO/ET theme began at an early age (https://trello.com/c/xk0nidWX/2103-%E2%96%B6%EF%B8%8F-dr-greer-describes-the-near-death-and-contact-experiences-of-his-youth), his increased attention to the subject did not develop until well into his medical career. At that stage, Dr. Greer's ongoing personal research into UFOs, ETs, and new energy systems led him to the knowledge that information and technologies surrounding these subjects were being kept from both the public and the highest ranks of our government, through decades of highly classified programs. It was this alarming realization that inspired Dr. Greer to begin his focused work on disclosure.\n\n> Dr. Greer initiated his work in the UFO/ET area by founding the Center for the Study of Extra-Terrestrial Intelligence (CSETI) (https://trello.com/c/kPV4R8gJ/903-%F0%9F%8C%90-sirius-disclosure-cseti) in 1990. CSETI was established as a diplomatic and research-based organization to make peaceful contact with extraterrestrial civilizations. Soon after, Dr. Greer founded https://trello.com/c/QM5mVK4f/2098-%F0%9F%8F%9B%EF%B8%8F-the-disclosure-project-%F0%9F%97%A3%EF%B8%8F, a nonprofit research initiative aimed at publicly disclosing the extensive and deeply classified information about UFOs, extraterrestrial intelligence, and advanced energy and propulsion systems.\n\n> While CSETI continued its diplomatic efforts throughout the 1990s, The Disclosure Project made substantial progress towards the release of classified UFO/ET information, culminating in the groundbreaking National Press Club Disclosure Event (https://trello.com/c/lZHwyO4m/810-2001-national-press-club-event-initiated-by-dr-steven-greers-disclosure-project) in May, 2001. During this event, over 20 military, government, intelligence, and corporate witnesses presented compelling testimony regarding the existence of extraterrestrial visitations as well as the reverse engineering of their energy and propulsion systems by classified government projects. The event reached an audience of over one billion people through both real-time streaming and coverage on top-tier, global media outlets.\n\n> In addition to Dr. Greer's ongoing efforts towards peaceful extraterrestrial contact and classified information disclosure, he has worked extensively to bring together scientists, inventors and leaders across the globe to advance new, clean technology energy systems. Dr. Greer is one of the world's most recognized strategists focused on transforming our civilization from one of fossil-fuel reliance to that of clean, free energy systems.\n\n> Dr. Greer has been seen and heard by vast audiences worldwide on CBS, the BBC, The Discovery Channel, The History Channel (including the Ancient Aliens series), Thrive and through a variety of global news outlets and social media networks. Millions have seen his groundbreaking documentaries, Sirius (2013) and Unacknowledged (2017), the latter of which yielded a companion book of the same transcripts:\n----------------\n\n• Ed on ET visitation, UFO crash recoveries, reverse-engineering, and abductions:\n▶️ https://youtu.be/LOHv1twCOqQ?t=376\n> Yes, there has been ET visitation, and may continue to be. There has been craft that, uh, have been recovered. There has been a certain amount of reverse engineering that has allowed some of these craft or some components to be duplicated. And that there are humanoids, uh from our planet, Earthlings, who are utilizing some of this equipment in certain ways. And that, perhaps a large part of the activity that's classified as UFO activity – abductions, and a whole host of this type of activity – may very well not be due to ET activity at all. I would suspect that if any is due to ET activity, it's a rather small part, and that a larger portion is due to humanoid-type activity, Earthling-type activity, in a very clandestine fashion.\n\n• Ed on the consideration of hostile intent, and abductions:\n▶️ https://youtu.be/LOHv1twCOqQ?t=497\n> I don't see anything that represents hostile intent. We see things that, uh, like abductions for example, that many would claim are hostile. Uh, to the extent that that may be true, I would more likely attribute it to some other cause.\n\n• on Dr. Greer's initiative and visits with the government:\n▶️ https://youtu.be/LOHv1twCOqQ?t=679\nEd:\n> Dr. Greer did indeed mount an initiative and did go to the – to Washington – did speak with high-level government people, did present some of the witnesses that we've talked about, uh... there, to give briefings, and has asked for congressional hearings on these matters. I attended and helped him with that. And I believe that's a very important effort, that we get, uh, congressional oversight of all this. But so far that hasn't happened. We briefed, uh, certain members of Congress, some of their staff, some of the people from the White House, we talked with people in the Pentagon. And in general it was well-received, and some were quite amazed at what they heard, but so far it hasn't resulted in any great activity.\n\nJames Fox:\n> Was this news to a lot of their ears?\n\nEd:\n> To some people, yes. Others, not really so much. Uh, but I will say that it led me to the belief that people in high-level government have very very little, if any information, valid information, about this. Most have no more knowledge than the man in the street. Representatives from uh, the intelligence section, they rattled the loop of the things we're talking about.\n\nJames Fox:\n> Does that come as a concern to you?\n\nEd:\n> Oh yes, it's a very great concern. The mystery craft descended, then flew from east to west direction for about 6 minutes. There was no sound and there were no strobe lights visible to the naked eye or through two night vision binoculars. Possibly an alleged plane with no strobes? or alleged cloaked extraterrestrial vehicle? One of many sightings that night.  \n\nPeter Chan also writes:\n> Team San Diego HICE also attend Joshua Tree October 15,16,17 and 18 in concert with Marcel Vidovic,  Greer and companies.   Neither parties knew our attendance plans.  The universe at play yet again. \nFriday (4 attend) site 1\nI saw the blue flag bulb above Ryan. \nJim Rawson had three knocks on his bedroom door at midnight. Freaked him out he left the next morning. \nThe three knocks on the door is a common occurrence I've recieved them twice. \nSaturday (6 attend) site 2\nMy phone emf goes off in the house and in the field\n@Cam Herndon sees double columns of light flash bulb third eye a ship. \n@Julian Mota and I sees flash bulbs separately same area. Confirmation by the radar detector via 👽👽👽.\nSteve sees the squiggle vertical light lines. \nSteve and I both see the huge white glowing object from the west goes straight then upwards. I figure the end of the show.   Then I was thinking it's all over then Ryan's radar detector goes off again. \nSunday (two attend) site 2\nI see flash bulbs\nRyan and I see the white glowing object the same as Saturday with Steve. \nI see an oval green glowing object flying north to south like a meteor without the tail looks like the object described by @Mark Sims 2012Nov. \nRyan plays practical joke leaves me behind drives off (not the first time) comes back I point upwards flash bulb then super bright flash bulb right above the car.\n\n----\n\nOn prerecordedness and the schedule\n----------------\n\nThis was definitely prerecorded given that Youtube doesn't have a function to premiere a livestream, only an uploaded video file; and it was in fact a premiere (as made clear by the usual Youtube premiere countdown shortly before the appointed start time).\n\nThe fact that it was prerecorded may explain why https://trello.com/c/aG9LsKs8/2091-%F0%9F%91%A9%F0%9F%8E%A4-demi-lovato-%F0%9F%8E%A4 's other event this day (https://twitter.com/ddlovato/status/1317160743339388929) at 8:45 PM PST wasn't a conflict; additionally, that event may have been prerecorded as well. That seems likely, in which case https://trello.com/c/aG9LsKs8/2091-%F0%9F%91%A9%F0%9F%8E%A4-demi-lovato-%F0%9F%8E%A4 was at Joshua Tree for likely all of 20/10/16.\n\nIt's also apparent that https://trello.com/c/aG9LsKs8/2091-%F0%9F%91%A9%F0%9F%8E%A4-demi-lovato-%F0%9F%8E%A4 was there for at least the evening and later on 20/10/15, given the text overlayed onto the sighting photos in those two attached sighting photo images, and that there was the (failed) attempt at a livestream that day.\nAccording to Greer's team, Greer was with Demi since 20/10/13 at Joshua Tree. They tried to go live several times, but \"at the house there was virtually no internet\" and Demi's people weren't okay with her being livestreamed (they \"must review and approve any content she puts out\"). There were other \"VIP/Celeb\" folks there who also did not want to be live.\n\nSupposedly the plan they came up with was to make contact for 5 nights in a row.\n\nKnown CSETI team members flew to Joshua Tree to participate in this event with https://trello.com/c/4dFMjJpF/2089-%F0%9F%91%A8%E2%9A%95%EF%B8%8F-dr-steven-greer-%F0%9F%A7%98%E2%99%82%EF%B8%8F and
